#: ../../D/ding.rst:13
msgid ""
"dinged: What happens when someone in authority gives you a minor bitching "
"about something, esp. something trivial. \"I was dinged for having a messy "
"desk.\""
msgstr "dinged：権威ある立場の誰かが、何か、特に些細なことについて軽い小言を言うときに起こること。「机が散らかっているとdingされた。」"
